701758f-a.title: Bronx: Seabury Place - Charlotte Street
701758f-a.text:
Seabury Place (horse and buggy thereon), between Charlotte and East
172nd Streets. The view is eastward across the Beck and Bathgate estates,
showing streets being laid out prior to the sale of the property at auction.
1905.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
